                    .col-lg-4.me-auto
                        h5 What is Jams?
                        p.lead As a server, we try to fill a void in the Minecraft server space, it is an open world vanilla server that is also not anarchy, think Hermitcraft but the players are less famous.
                        p.load We have no majorly gameplay-altering plugins, including teleportation, playerhomes, no skills system, and no out of game economy.
                        p.load We also do not allow Staff members to abuse their power and spawn in OP items. They should be just like normal players when not doing staff work.
                        p.load We are 100% Minecraft EULA complaint and have no pay to win features. While we do have a patreon with many great perks, subscribing to it will not put you at an advantage over others.
                        p.load We allow all vanilla glitches to be used in game such as TNT duping, bedrock breaking, headless pistons, stasis chambers, composter xraying, infinite zombie villager cures, nether roof travel, and villager trade resetting.
                        p.load However, we do not allow item duping. The server runs on Purpur (a speedy server) without any dodgy plugins so this is pretty much impossible to do anyway. Carpet, rail, TNT and gravity block duping is considered a vanilla glitch as above and is allowed.
                        p.load We do our best to ensure your bases and items are safe with efficient moderation, rollback and report systems that replace what land claims would do on a conventional server.


